{"tid":1863201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"逼華維迪落台？美斯網上反擊艾比度","createTime":"2020-02-05T04:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T09:59:06.000Z","uid":31626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9c1706307e3da1be1d219842ee969882347860e5","tid":1863201,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】巴塞隆拿内訌加劇，球星美斯在社交網站質問體育總監艾比度，要求對方澄清誰逼前教練華維迪下台。<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿日前爆出操練發生衝突後，首席球星美斯（Lionel Messi）也與體育總監艾比度展開隔空内訌，事緣艾比度之前在訪問中，提到有球員出工不出力，逼前教練華維迪離去，「更衣室雖然和諧，但我作為前球員發覺氣氛不對，於是告訴會方必須有所行動。」艾比度說。<br />\n<br />\n美斯對此番言論十分不滿，在社交網站反擊：「我不喜歡這樣的事情，每個人都要為自己的決定負責。球員為場上表現負責，我們也是最先察覺球隊出問題的人。那些負責體育管理的人，應該知道自己的責任所在，作出自己的決定。」<br />\n<br />\n美斯言下之意是，球隊高層決定換帥的話，就不要把責任推給球員。「最後，既然有人提到球員的行為，請給出確實的姓名！不然，他的言論就缺乏說服力。」美斯輕易把壓力交到艾比度的一方。"},{"pid":"c9b878b231bdc26739d44bf60c4cd8e7f096112b","tid":1863201,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffbda8a150bd7ace300501132c521025a0a86e8","tid":1863201,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"球皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206b38f92ab5aa39a7a6cead1fdfb680e55cd344","tid":1863201,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"華維迪是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa07c54fe86b761bf3d2468695d52176b6d99a1","tid":1863201,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"206b38f92ab5aa39a7a6cead1fdfb680e55cd344","tid":1863201,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"華維迪是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"我已經mark晒反華份子   準備逐個清算"},{"pid":"63a8f826a0f0e8193503989e750b800f1302e611","tid":1863201,"uid":172226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"哩鋪撐美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩度係咪有個咩咩中轉英既會員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab946af5b33cebc563c03e05934516c8fedfb04e","tid":1863201,"uid":200801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"美斯"},{"pid":"04c4cb90b560c157c9c7e3e7fa5bac05db7bd0c2","tid":1863201,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"邊個教都一樣架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6575172ce3a28c6fb3faa327eed88fe6a87f0c97","tid":1863201,"uid":23140,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"艾比度唔死得仲要痴埋六冠 依家有份工打下<br />\n好心就出少句聲 仲要單打當年carry自己果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b23e55d4daa2d68e4464bbafc5e5e68200e477","tid":1863201,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9ce41f7d23276d42ed65489dcf8a4d29e42101","tid":1863201,"uid":203961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"美斯出名迷華啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}